thread.title_full: Westminster Teak reviewed by Maine and FL gal

author: Maine and FL gal
title: Maine and FL gal
text: This is our 2nd purchase for additional pieces of teak furniture. It's quality furniture at a reasonable cost! And it's nice that you send temporary cushion covers until your custom order is completed! This way to enjoy your purchase right away. And I love your sales. Thank you.
